## Which License Do I Need?

| Your Situation | License | Cost |
|----------------|---------|------|
| Academic research (willing to share modifications) | AGPL-3.0-or-later | Free |
| Open source project | AGPL-3.0-or-later | Free |
| Personal/educational use | AGPL-3.0-or-later | Free |
| Non-profit (willing to share modifications) | AGPL-3.0-or-later | Free |
| Company (willing to open-source your application) | AGPL-3.0-or-later | Free |
| Company (want to keep code proprietary) | Commercial | Contact us |
| SaaS provider (don't want to share backend code) | Commercial | Contact us |
| Embedded in proprietary product | Commercial | Contact us |

